{"tid":43743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人牙骹同我一樣","createTime":"2016-12-17T16:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T05:00:04.000Z","uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1351b100cb55d9ac2440626879817bd90dd43a1f","tid":43743,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"打個喊露又會有啪一聲.. 有時食D硬少少既野好似冬菜都會有... 我就係左邊面..右邊無<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我本身有箍牙..問過牙醫..佢話好似牙骹就好似D關節咁(啪手指, 波羅蓋行行下啪一聲, 大脾內則 , 頸ETC)有時都會啪一聲啦<br />\n<br />\n我有做比佢睇 ..因為有時要真係噤一噤入去先知有個虛位同埋有聲.. 有時打個喊露都有<br />\n不過又唔知點解唔係成日發生, 但我就成日形住形住... 其實係有無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n我做過針炙又好左一排.. 無做又係咁...<br />\n枕住枕住都幾年了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無爸打. 絲打同我一樣問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d766e1757a5a267630621a89941379da8d3f1927","tid":43743,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810d8834148e94c1d6b97ea61fcfee0f31a5ab8e","tid":43743,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:08:02.000Z","msg":"我，我都問過牙醫，就係個骹位鬆咗，如果要整返好就要做手術，如果唔影響生活就無所謂，但個軟骨易磨蝕"},{"pid":"a9656e1f8c5ba4e61a17aaad09859fe9f3217b4c","tid":43743,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我，我都問過牙醫，就係個骹位鬆咗，如果要整返好就要做手術，如果唔影響生活就無所謂，但個軟骨易磨蝕</blockquote><br />\n你有冇成日形住形住...<br />\n<br />\n佢一時無野一時有野先煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccba37840cff4d0f1f55eb3fcfcf3fc990be51a","tid":43743,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ab8a561b6b905721ab8c7abf2f78c01fac9aee","tid":43743,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecb7a927288d445bcc22aaa0ec4d5baf627bc6a","tid":43743,"uid":6439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"叫人用雞脾打一打自己"},{"pid":"4fa64d132a84beedd9a96e019bbef150d989b56e","tid":43743,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}